<th style="padding:0.2em 1.0em 0.2em 0.2em; background:transparent; line-height:1.2em; text-align:left; font-size:90%;">Title</th>
<td class="" style="padding:0.2em; line-height:1.3em; vertical-align:middle; font-size:90%;">Editor-in-Chief of <a href="/wiki/Skeptic_(U.S._magazine)" title="Skeptic (U.S. magazine)"><i>Skeptic</i></a> and Adjunct professor in Economics at <a href="/wiki/Claremont_Graduate_University" title="Claremont Graduate University">Claremont Graduate University</a></td>
