<li><i><a href="/wiki/Penn_%26_Teller" title="Penn &amp; Teller">Penn &amp; Teller</a>'s <a href="/wiki/Bullshit!" title="Bullshit!" class="mw-redirect">Bullshit!</a></i> on "<a href="/wiki/List_of_Bullshit!_episodes" title="List of Bullshit! episodes" class="mw-redirect">The Bible: Fact or Fiction</a>?" (2004)<sup id="cite_ref-ShermerBible_17-3" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-ShermerBible-17" title=""><span>[</span>18<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
