<li><i><a href="/wiki/Why_People_Believe_Weird_Things:_Pseudoscience,_Superstition,_and_Other_Confusions_of_Our_Time" title="Why People Believe Weird Things: Pseudoscience, Superstition, and Other Confusions of Our Time">Why People Believe Weird Things: Pseudoscience, Superstition, and Other Confusions of Our Time</a>.</i> (1997, 2nd Revision edition 2002) <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0805070893" class="internal">ISBN 0-8050-7089-3</a></li>
