<li><i><a href="/wiki/Denying_History:_Who_Says_the_Holocaust_Never_Happened_and_Why_Do_They_Say_It%3F" title="Denying History: Who Says the Holocaust Never Happened and Why Do They Say It?" class="mw-redirect">Denying History: Who Says the Holocaust Never Happened and Why Do They Say It?</a></i> 2002 <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0520234693" class="internal">ISBN 0-520-23469-3</a></li>
<li><i>In Darwin's Shadow: The Life and Science of Alfred Russel Wallace: A Biographical Study on the Psychology of History</i> 2002 <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0195148304" class="internal">ISBN 0-19-514830-4</a></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Science_of_Good_and_Evil:_Why_People_Cheat,_Gossip,_Care,_Share,_and_Follow_the_Golden_Rule" title="The Science of Good and Evil: Why People Cheat, Gossip, Care, Share, and Follow the Golden Rule" class="mw-redirect">The Science of Good and Evil: Why People Cheat, Gossip, Care, Share, and Follow the Golden Rule</a></i> 2004 <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0805075208" class="internal">ISBN 0-8050-7520-8</a></li>
