<li><i>Secrets of Mental Math: The Mathemagician's Guide to Lightning Calculation and Amazing Math Tricks</i> 2006 <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780307338402" class="internal">ISBN 978-0307338402</a></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Why_Darwin_Matters:_The_Case_Against_Intelligent_Design" title="Why Darwin Matters: The Case Against Intelligent Design" class="mw-redirect">Why Darwin Matters: The Case Against Intelligent Design</a></i> 2006 <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780805081213" class="internal">ISBN 978-0-8050-8121-3</a></li>
